VALUES ('100 RBH', 'The Oracle Sisters is a Paris-based indie rock, indie folk, and indie pop band formed in 2017. The band consists of multi-instrumentalists Lewis Lazar, Christopher Willatt, and Julia Johansen. They were featured as one of NME''s Essential New Artists for 2019.
