VALUES ('Gummineni Vijay', 'Vijay Prakash (born 21 February 1976) is an Indian Playback singer and Music director from Karnataka. He has given his voice for predominantly Kannada, Tamil, and Telugu language films, in addition to Hindi, Malayalam and Marathi language films. He has also performed shows with Zakir Hussain. Prakash won the Karnataka Government''s ''Best Playback Singer'' award for the year 2016 for the song "Nammooralli Chaligaladalli" from the film Beautiful Manasugalu.
