To his credit, he tried to create his own identity as a playback singer and tried not to follow the K. L. Saigal style of singing. Durrani was notable for sad songs, Romantic songs, Patriotic songs, Qur''an Khani, Qawwalis, Ghazals and Bhajans. He was also one of the first Muslim singers to sing Hindu Devotionals. G. M. Durrani was also the old', NULL, 0);

